news.title: About 20 lakh buildings in Kerala were out of property tax net in 2021
news.para: Local bodies exempted 19.8 lakh residential buildings below 660sq ft from paying property tax in the state, accounting for 13% of total buildings as per the data collected in 2021.

news.title: Housr acquires StayAbode, enters Bengaluru market
news.para: The price point will range from Rs 14,000- 24,000 for twin sharing and Rs 25,000-50,000 for single occupancy in Housr co-living.

news.title: PropShare raises Rs 367 crore from WestBridge Capital & Pravega Ventures
news.para: "By partnering with WestBridge Capital, we plan to grow to over $1 billion in transacted assets on the platform by expanding into newer geographies and property types, while keeping technology and our investors at the core of our offering," said Hashim Khan, CTO, Propshare.
